{"tid":2368122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港水上飛機公司｜250元體驗香港空中暢遊 18分鐘直送大灣區","createTime":"2021-01-16T02:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T04:01:40.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8180c027ea3638204c0d72457832d598b9626cd3","tid":2368122,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:18:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">香港水上飛機公司｜250元體驗香港空中暢遊 18分鐘直送大灣區</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vw8D4kS8DbljJ-WYIKhxKc3hEic=/1591x885/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YUBNV4ZU3JGKDHUDFLFAOEN52I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvw8D4kS8DbljJ-WYIKhxKc3hEic%3D%2F1591x885%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYUBNV4ZU3JGKDHUDFLFAOEN52I.jpg&h=f0246786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yb9acBmoNZNFEjCmiWgaihqmD0Q=/799x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G5F2L4VBNBHEVND7HYRPLRWBBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyb9acBmoNZNFEjCmiWgaihqmD0Q%3D%2F799x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG5F2L4VBNBHEVND7HYRPLRWBBU.jpg&h=db384745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港首間水上飛機航空公司上線啦。名為水上飛機（香港）航空的本地公司，計劃投資逾一億元發展香港及大灣區業務，主打觀光、包機、空中的士等服務，暫時訂價$250起，珠海、茂名、湛江、汕頭等設上落站，只要簡單預約便可把你直送大灣區。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，該公司首階段服務集中在香港，預料在西九文化中心以及鯉魚門一帶起飛，暢遊維港景色，位位$250起。另外該公司更會提供空中的士服務，價格$800起，市民可用該公司推出手機應用程式呼召服務，想去哪裏都可以。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人之一的張敬龍初步構想&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n閱讀全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210114/P6TKSQPMMZAH3CQZPSYD66J4L4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210114%2FP6TKSQPMMZAH3CQZPSYD66J4L4%2